This is the package "ecrc-nppp" for generating CRC journal articles using the Elsevier LaTeX document class elsarticle.
The package incorporates customisations for the Elsevier CRC journal 
Nuclear and Particle Physics Proceedings
This version 1.2 dated 8 January 2015 (patch version 08 February 2011)
=======================================================================

The following files are included:
* The elsarticle document class, elsarticle.cls
* The documentation, elsdoc.pdf
* A bibliographic style file for the numbered reference style, elsarticle-num.bst
* The package file for Elsevier CRC, ecrc.sty
* Sample journal logo files elsevier-logo-3p.pdf, SDlogo-3p.pdf
(All the above are also available at http://www.elsevier.com/latex)

* A template manuscript file, nuppp-template.tex

To use:
1. Unpack all the files into the same folder
2. Edit the manuscript file nppp-template.tex according to the instructions in that file, and save with a new name
3. Compile with PDFLaTeX (and BibTeX if desired)

****************************************************
*                                                  *
* Important note on usage                          *
* -----------------------                          *
* The template file must be compiled with PDFLaTeX *
* Using standard LaTeX will not work!              *
*                                                  *
****************************************************

=======================================================================
NB The ecrc.sty package is currently under evaluation.
We welcome feedback, comments and suggestions from our authors.
